snippet.title: Zelda A Link to the Past SNES Commercial - Retro Game Trailers
snippet.description:
This legend of zelda ad is a fever dream and you have to wonder if that's because thre was so much lead paint back then or if that's just how ads worked before the internet

Watch more trailers here!
